{
  "texts": [
    "In the subsequent section, we detail the configurations of the different datasets and the accuracy and precision metrics utilized to evaluate the performance of our approach, DEMASQ.",
    "Benchmark DatasetOur benchmark dataset is created using a variety of datasets spanning multiple domains, as mentioned above.",
    "To generate the samples from ChatGPT, we made use of the queries gathered by Guo et al. [23] that also presented the corresponding human answer, then through the use of OpenAI's API 2 we queried the latest version of GPT-3.5 at this time (gpt-3.5-turbo) requesting 3 different answers for each input question.",
    "Due to the limitation of the available data and the reported unstable behavior of ChatGPT [40], we assumed that the API would properly perform only with English prompts, therefore only querying for answer in this language.",
    "The dataset comprises a total of 134,178 unique samples, with 59,214 responses generated by humans and 74,964 responses generated by the ChatGPT model."
  ]
}